                        <interp inst="t18350615-1545-verdict-2" type="verdictSubcategory" value="withRecommendation"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>. Aged 17. <hi rend="italic">Recommended to mercy by the Jury.</hi>
               </p>
